title: Jumpstart
description:
Educational software for children. 26 different programs designed for ages 9 months to 11 years. Files are provided as disc images in either .iso or .bin/.cue format. MagicDisc has been included for your convenience as an option to mount the images onto a virtual drive. Please share this release as long as possible and remember to enjoy it with your children. Thank You
